5. Hropachhana Raihria liata 
Odyh 82 hria theipa a cha tahpa khai tawhta a ry la he paraopa ta 
Hropachhana Raihria Bie liahmarihpazy cha 
1) Chyhsa Hropachhana a cha.
2) Chyhsa Thlahpalohna a cha.
3) Baona atotuhpazy no-hah vaina  a cha.
4) Hnabeiseihna pa-ina a cha.
5) Ama peimawh chaipa Hmodah piena a cha.
6) Ama peimawh chaipa Daihti liata piena a cha.
7) Pathluapachhaihna y leipa ta raina a cha.
Hropachhana raihria liata eima zydua a cha-ao chyuh suh vy tahpa he bai hri thei awpa
